{
  "version": "0.4",
  "title": "XCP Home Part 3 - Checkerboard Layouts",
  "type": "page",
  "content": [
    {
      "id": "checkerboard-1",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Checkerboard Section 1 - Image Left",
        "layout": "full_width",
        "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "60", "right": "0", "bottom": "60", "left": "0"}
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "checker-1-image",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 50,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100,
            "background_background": "classic",
            "background_image": {"url": "[uc_local]assets/images/checkerboard-1.jpg"},
            "background_size": "cover",
            "background_position": "center",
            "min_height": {"unit": "px", "size": 500}
          },
          "elements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "checker-1-content",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 50,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100,
            "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "60", "right": "60", "bottom": "60", "left": "60"},
            "content_position": "middle"
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "checker-1-heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Elevate Your Brand Beyond the Expected",
                "header_size": "h2",
                "typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 36}
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "checker-1-text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p style='font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8;'>Your brand isn't like everyone else's—so why should your imagery be?</p><p style='font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8;'>Whether you're building recognition, launching something new, or repositioning for growth, your visuals should command attention and spark the kind of connection that turns casual browsers into devoted followers.</p><p style='font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8;'>Authentic branding photography captures what words can't: the energy, the values, the unmistakable essence that makes you unforgettable to your ideal audience.</p>"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "checkerboard-2",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Checkerboard Section 2 - Image Right",
        "layout": "full_width",
        "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "60", "right": "0", "bottom": "60", "left": "0"}
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "checker-2-content",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 50,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100,
            "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "60", "right": "60", "bottom": "60", "left": "60"},
            "content_position": "middle"
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "checker-2-heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Tell Stories That Resonate, Not Just Look Good",
                "header_size": "h2",
                "typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 36}
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "checker-2-text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p style='font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8;'>Your audience doesn't just want pretty pictures—they want to feel something.</p><p style='font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8;'>Documentary-style imagery brings depth and authenticity to your brand story. It captures real moments, genuine emotion, and the human side of what you do. This is where connection happens.</p><p style='font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8;'>When your ideal clients see themselves reflected in your story, they don't just engage—they invest. In you. In what you offer. In the transformation you make possible.</p>"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "checker-2-image",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 50,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100,
            "background_background": "classic",
            "background_image": {"url": "[uc_local]assets/images/checkerboard-2.jpg"},
            "background_size": "cover",
            "background_position": "center",
            "min_height": {"unit": "px", "size": 500}
          },
          "elements": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
